Class AbstractIdentifier<IdentifierType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • bio.singa.features.identifiers.model.AbstractIdentifier<IdentifierType>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifier<IdentifierType>, Feature<IdentifierType>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChEBIIdentifier, ECNumber, ENAAccessionNumber, GoTerm, InChIKey, NCBITaxonomyIdentifier, PDBIdentifier, PDBLigandIdentifier, PfamIdentifier, PubChemIdentifier, RefSeqIdentifier, SimpleStringIdentifier, UniProtEntryName, UniProtIdentifier

    public abstract class AbstractIdentifier<IdentifierType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Identifier<IdentifierType>, Feature<IdentifierType>
    The most basic, abstract implementation of Identifier. Validates the identifier during instantiation, also overrides equals, hashcode and toString methods.
